What's new in this version

• Choose how Pause watches your time: Usage access (recommended) or Accessibility.
• Clear, plain-English explanation of exactly what Pause reads (only the app name + time), what it can't (your screen, messages, keystrokes), and that nothing leaves your phone.
• Personalise the reminder: your own image + message, sticker-style text, and witty presets.
• Real app icons in the picker, custom intervals, and lots of polish.
